  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK744">
<l>ciṟukāppiṟ pēriṭatta tāki yuṟupakai</l>
<l>yūkka maḻippa taraṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fort is that which has an extensive space within, but only small places to be guarded, and such as can destroy the courage of besieging foes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
